    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About This Example Set",
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 10, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Network Port Inventory\n\nTrack every switch port across your network with speed value mappings, live status coloring, and one-click access to device management interfaces.\n\n### Features demonstrated\n\n- 🔢 **Value mappings** — 1000/10000/100000 → 1G/10G/100G\n- 🟢 **Row coloring** — UP=green, DOWN=red, DISABLED=gray\n- 🔗 **Clickthrough** — click a device name to open its management interface (hidden URL column)\n- 📐 **Column widths** — MAC (150px), IP (120px), Description (30% wide)\n- 🔍 **Search** — find any device by name, IP, or MAC\n\n[Open Full Topology Table →](/d/dt-network-topology)",
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "briangann-datatable-panel",
      "title": "Topology Preview",
      "datasource": { "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INFINITY}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "1000": { "text": "1G", "index": 0 }, "10000": { "text": "10G", "index": 1 }, "100000": { "text": "100G", "index": 2 } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DISABLED", "index": 0 }, "1": { "text": "UP", "index": 1 }, "2": { "text": "DOWN", "index": 2 } } }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 14, "x": 10, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
